data.description: 72 Hour Kick-out. This beautiful River Grove South Merritt Island gem is a 4-bed, 3-bath, 3-car garage home w/  a multi-generational style split floor plan. It boasts abundant natural light from large windows, 10' & 12' ceilings, crown molding, & wood style tile/wood floors/carpet throughout. Notable upgrades include a 2020 roof w/radiant barrier & R30 insulation, 2021 electrical panel to include new ties w/ a ground replacement, & a 2021 water heater. An updated kitchen w/ stainless steel appliances & center island is open to a breakfast nook & a large family room that is perfect for gatherings. The spacious primary suite features wood flooring, double walk-in closets, & a primary bath that includes a large soaking tub, shower, & separate sinks/vanities. A 2nd primary suite offers privacy with a tub-shower combo. The secondary bedrooms share a guest bath shower w/ convenient outdoor access. The open floor plan incl. formal dining & living areas, w/ French doors leading to a screened patio. The 3-car garage provides ample space for storage and work areas. Entertain on the enclosed patio in the large, private fenced backyard, and enjoy a partial distant river view from the front. Security system equipment incl. The neighborhood offers a private dock on the Indian River w/ stunning sunset views. Conveniently located near beaches, schools, PAFB, Kennedy Space Center, & so much more! Call for a showing today!!
